properties.name: springfox.documentation.auto-startup
properties.description: Flag that indicates if springfox should auto start scanning services

properties.name: springfox.documentation.enabled
properties.description: Flag that indicates if springfox should scan services to produce specifications.

properties.name: springfox.documentation.open-api.enabled
properties.description: Flag that disables openApi related beans

properties.name: springfox.documentation.swagger-ui.base-url
properties.description: Base url for swagger-ui. For e.g. setting it to /documentation will put swagger-ui at /documentation/swagger-ui/index.html

properties.name: springfox.documentation.swagger-ui.enabled
properties.description: Flag that disables swagger-ui from being resource-handled. No swagger-ui when this is false.

properties.name: springfox.documentation.swagger.v2.enabled
properties.description: Flag that disables swagger 2 related beans

properties.name: springfox.documentation.swagger.v2.host
properties.description: Host name to use for swagger 2 specification

properties.name: springfox.documentation.swagger.v2.use-model-v3
properties.description: Flag that toggles between generating models using v3.0.0 of the library or the 2.9.x version of the library. This flag can be changed to false, if v3.0.0 is not working as expected.
